#: main_19.cpp:3
msgid "Start next time in normal screen"
msgstr "Anza wakati mwingine kwenye skrini ya kawaida"

#: main_19.cpp:7
msgid "Start next time in full screen mode"
msgstr "Anza wakati mwingine katika hali ya skrini nzima"

#: main_19.cpp:9
msgid "If you exit the program from the menu, then the program"
msgstr "Ukitoka kwenye programu kutoka kwenye menyu, basi programu"

#: main_19.cpp:11
msgid "will restart in normal 2d screen mode."
msgstr "itaanza upya katika hali ya kawaida ya skrini ya 2D."

#: main_19.cpp:13
msgid "If you exit the program from the engine window toolbar,"
msgstr "Ukitoka kwenye programu kutoka kwenye upau wa vidhibiti wa dirisha la injini,"

#: main_19.cpp:15
msgid "then the program will restart in full screen mode."
msgstr "kisha programu itaanza upya katika hali ya skrini nzima."

#: main_19.cpp:17
msgid "Alternative - click to take back the reply move and play an alternative move instead."
msgstr "Mbadala - bofya ili kurejesha hoja ya jibu na ucheze hoja mbadala badala yake."

#: main_19.cpp:19
msgid "To over-ride the default behaviour of this option"
msgstr "Ili kubatilisha tabia chaguo-msingi ya chaguo hili"

#: main_19.cpp:21
msgid "Hold down < Ctrl > for the next alternative move in the list"
msgstr "Shikilia < Ctrl > kwa hoja mbadala inayofuata kwenye orodha"

#: main_19.cpp:23
msgid "Hold down < Shift > for a random alternative move"
msgstr "Shikilia chini < Shift > kwa hoja mbadala isiyo ya kawaida"

#: main_19.cpp:25
msgid "Hold down < Ctrl > and < Shift > for the best alternative move"
msgstr "Shikilia chini < Ctrl > na < Shift > kwa hoja mbadala bora"

#: main_19.cpp:27
msgid "on the keyboard, select < File > < Exit 3d > from the main menu,"
msgstr "kwenye kibodi, chagua < Faili > < Toka 3d > kutoka kwenye menyu kuu,"

#: main_19.cpp:29
msgid "To exit the program from the 3d screen, select < File > < Exit program >"
msgstr "Ili kutoka kwenye programu kutoka kwenye skrini ya 3D, chagua < Faili > < Toka kwenye programu >"

#: main_19.cpp:31
msgid "If the want to the program to restart in 3d graphics mode next time,"
msgstr "Ikiwa unataka programu ianze upya katika hali ya michoro ya 3D wakati mwingine,"

#: main_19.cpp:33
msgid "then hold down the < Ctrl > key when you select this option."
msgstr "kisha shikilia kitufe cha < Ctrl > unapochagua chaguo hili."

#: main_19.cpp:35
msgid "Adjourned games  -  Click to load a previously adjourned game."
msgstr "Michezo Iliyoahirishwa - Bonyeza ili kupakia mchezo ulioahirishwa awali."

#: main_19.cpp:37
msgid "Load an adjourned game"
msgstr "Pakia mchezo ulioahirishwa"

#: main_19.cpp:39
msgid "Adjourn game"
msgstr "Mchezo wa kuahirisha"

#: main_19.cpp:41
msgid "Open the Adjourned game dialog box"
msgstr "Fungua kisanduku cha mazungumzo cha mchezo ulioahirishwa"

#: main_19.cpp:43
msgid "Adjourned games"
msgstr "Michezo iliyoahirishwa"

#: main_19.cpp:45
msgid "Adjourned game file name"
msgstr "Jina la faili ya mchezo lililoahirishwa"

#: main_19.cpp:47
msgid "Select adjourned game .pgn filename"
msgstr "Chagua jina la faili la mchezo ulioahirishwa .pgn"

#: main_19.cpp:49
msgid "Load"
msgstr "Mzigo"

#: main_19.cpp:51
msgid "Enter the PGN adjourn game file name"
msgstr "Ingiza jina la faili ya mchezo wa kuahirisha PGN"

#: main_19.cpp:52
msgid "Save the current game as adjouned"
msgstr "Hifadhi mchezo wa sasa kama ulivyopangwa"

#: main_19.cpp:53
msgid "Load the adjourned game as current"
msgstr "Pakia mchezo ulioahirishwa kama wa sasa"

#: main_19.cpp:55
msgid "This dialog box allows you to adjourn a game and restart it later."
msgstr "Kisanduku hiki cha mazungumzo hukuruhusu kuahirisha mchezo na kuuanzisha tena baadaye."

#: main_19.cpp:57
msgid "Click the < Save > button to save the current game."
msgstr "Bonyeza kitufe cha < Hifadhi > ili kuhifadhi mchezo wa sasa."

#: main_19.cpp:59
msgid "You can them choose the PGN file for saving the game in"
msgstr "Unaweza kuchagua faili ya PGN kwa ajili ya kuhifadhi mchezo ndani"

#: main_19.cpp:61
msgid "and then you can enter the game details."
msgstr "na kisha unaweza kuingiza maelezo ya mchezo."

#: main_19.cpp:63
msgid "Click the < Load > button to load a previously stored game."
msgstr "Bonyeza kitufe cha < Pakia > ili kupakia mchezo uliohifadhiwa hapo awali."

#: main_19.cpp:65
msgid "As before you choose the PGN file to load the game from,"
msgstr "Kama kabla ya kuchagua faili ya PGN ya kupakia mchezo,"

#: main_19.cpp:67
msgid "and then you can pick the game that you want."
msgstr "na kisha unaweza kuchagua mchezo unaotaka."

#: main_19.cpp:69
msgid "If you click < Ok > the game will be loaded, ready for playing."
msgstr "Ukibofya < Sawa > mchezo utapakiwa, tayari kwa kuchezwa."

#: main_19.cpp:71
msgid "Then pick < Play white > or < Play black > depending on which colour"
msgstr "Kisha chagua < Cheza nyeupe > au < Cheza nyeusi > kulingana na rangi gani"

#: main_19.cpp:73
msgid "you had in the adjourned game."
msgstr "ulikuwa nao katika mchezo ulioahirishwa."

#: main_19.cpp:75
msgid "Adjourned games can also be restarted from the rated game dialog box."
msgstr "Michezo iliyoahirishwa inaweza pia kuanzishwa upya kutoka kwenye kisanduku cha mazungumzo cha mchezo kilichokadiriwa."

#: main_19.cpp:77
msgid "If you load a game from there, it will be automatically ready for play,"
msgstr "Ukipakia mchezo kutoka hapo, utakuwa tayari kiotomatiki kwa ajili ya kucheza,"

#: main_19.cpp:79
msgid "although your clock will not start until you make a move."
msgstr "ingawa saa yako haitaanza hadi utakapofanya hatua."

#: main_19.cpp:81
msgid "Adjourn game dialog box"
msgstr "Kisanduku cha mazungumzo cha kuahirisha mchezo"

#: main_19.cpp:83
msgid "Error writing clock config file"
msgstr "Hitilafu katika kuandika faili ya usanidi wa saa"

#: main_19.cpp:85
msgid "Invalid PGN file name"
msgstr "Jina batili la faili ya PGN"

#: main_19.cpp:87
msgid "Cannot open clock config file"
msgstr "Haiwezi kufungua faili ya usanidi wa saa"

#: main_19.cpp:89
msgid "Adjourned game saved"
msgstr "Mchezo ulioahirishwa umehifadhiwa"

#: main_19.cpp:91
msgid "Adjourned game loaded"
msgstr "Mchezo ulioahirishwa umepakiwa"

#: main_19.cpp:93
msgid "Error reading clock configuration file, operation cancelled"
msgstr "Hitilafu ya kusoma faili ya usanidi wa saa, operesheni imeghairiwa"

#: main_19.cpp:95
msgid "Could not open clock configuration file, operation cancelled"
msgstr "Haikuweza kufungua faili ya usanidi wa saa, operesheni imeghairiwa"

#: main_19.cpp:97
msgid "Could not find clock configuration file, operation cancelled"
msgstr "Haikuweza kupata faili ya usanidi wa saa, operesheni imeghairiwa"

#: main_19.cpp:99
msgid "Press < Ok > to transfer the game to the board"
msgstr "Bonyeza < Sawa > ili kuhamisha mchezo kwenye ubao"

#: main_19.cpp:101
msgid "Adjourned game options"
msgstr "Chaguzi za mchezo ulioahirishwa"
